milestones.description: Lance Cairns has broken the record for most ducks (5) in ODIs for NZ, going past Hadlee's 4
Vic Marks has taken the most five-wicket hauls (2) in ODIs for ENG, going past Mike Hendrick's record
David Gower has broken the record for most catches (25) in ODIs for ENG, going past Ian Botham's 24
